            <p style="color: rgb(63, 61, 61);">Alredy have an account? <span><a href="/login" style="text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: blue;margin-left: 4px;">Sign in</a></span></p>
             
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-3">
              <div class="form-outline me-2" style="flex: 1;">
